  "title": "Forklift Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Load/Unload goods from vehicles and stack them in assigned places 从货车上装卸货物并将其堆放在指定位置</li><li>Accurate picking and packing of released orders 准确拣选和包装</li><li>Receive and inspect incoming/outgoing stock 接受并检查和盘点进货/出货库存</li><li>Housekeeping and cleanliness 确保工作环境安全与清洁</li><li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned 其他临时职责</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess valid forklift license 拥有有效的叉车执照</li><li>Communicate with customers in basic English and Mandarin 能用基本英语和普通话和顾客沟通</li><li>For both genders 男女皆宜</li><li>Secondary education level 中学教育</li><li>Fit and Healthy 身体健康</li><li>Only Singaporean or SPR holders, no quota for foreigners 新加坡人或永久居民可申请</li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Tuas (2-way bus provided) 地点：大士 （提供往返厂车接送）</li><li>Salary will commensurate according to experience 薪资将根据经验而定</li><li>Variable Bonus & AWS 可变奖金和年度工资补贴</li><li>Mobile phone & Transport Allowances 手机和交通津贴</li><li>Working days:</li><li>Monday to Friday 星期一到星期五 ：8.45am to 5.30pm</li><li>Saturday 周六 ：8.45am to 12.45pm </li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@beni.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">recruit@beni.com.sg</a> or call6862-4001 ext.103. 有意者，请把简历发送 <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@beni.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">recruit@beni.com.sg</a> 或致电6862-4001ext.103</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>我们只会通知被入取者。</p>",
